# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:6
translate chinese u19a1s2_a6f3ef5c:

    # "Mom leads me into her husband's workshop."
    "妈妈领我走进她丈夫的工作室。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:7
translate chinese u19a1s2_124d5993:

    # "It looks so similar to Dad's workshop in the basement back home. Papers everywhere. Clutter. Devices with no clue as to their function."
    "这里和家里地下室爸爸的工作室简直一模一样。到处都是纸张。杂乱无章。还有些完全看不出用途的装置。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:8
translate chinese u19a1s2_14ba12b5:

    # rm "Honey, do you have a second? I met somebody out on Sky Hill who I want you to meet."
    rm "亲爱的，你有空吗？我在天山遇到了个人，想让你见见他。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:11
translate chinese u19a1s2_69aac6f3:

    # "Dad" "Of course, love. I always have time for you."
    "Dad" "当然，亲爱的。我随时都有时间陪你。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:14
translate chinese u19a1s2_a9790a94:

    # rm "This is [pcname]. He told me he's here looking for his father."
    rm "这位是[pcname]。他说他来这里是想找他父亲的。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:17
translate chinese u19a1s2_71a936b7:

    # rm "He was up on Sky Hill, completely naked, freezing to death."
    rm "他在天山那儿，全身赤裸，冻得快要死了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:18
translate chinese u19a1s2_95e8533c:

    # rm "I thought maybe he could borrow some of your clothes and we could help him look for his father."
    rm "我想也许他可以借点你的衣服，我们还能帮他找找他父亲。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:21
translate chinese u19a1s2_0d97ce91:

    # "Dad" "Good idea, honey. Why don't you go find him some clothes from my closet."
    "Dad" "好主意，亲爱的。你去我的衣柜里给他找些衣服吧。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:22
translate chinese u19a1s2_002ec574:

    # rm "Is everything okay? You're acting rather odd."
    rm "你没事吧？你今天有点反常。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:23
translate chinese u19a1s2_873e8939:

    # "Dad" "No, I'm okay. Everything's fine."
    "Dad" "没，我没事。一切都好。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:24
translate chinese u19a1s2_3ad73c30:

    # rm "Okay. I'll go get him some clothes then."
    rm "好吧。那我去给他拿点衣服。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:27
translate chinese u19a1s2_e82630e8:

    # "When Mom walks out the door, Dad looks at me for a moment, keeping the same blank expression."
    "当妈妈走出门时，爸爸盯着我看了一会儿，脸上依然是那副茫然的表情。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:30
translate chinese u19a1s2_83336efc:

    # "Then he rushes forward and wraps his arms around me, pulling me into a tight hug."
    "接着他猛地冲过来，双臂环住我，紧紧地抱住了我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:31
translate chinese u19a1s2_84b9568c:

    # "Dad" "I'm so sorry, Son. I'm so sorry that I left you."
    "Dad" "对不起，儿子。真的很抱歉，我当初离开你了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:32
translate chinese u19a1s2_1811a5be:

    # pc "What the hell happened, Dad? What are you doing here?"
    pc "到底发生了什么事，爸爸？你来这儿干什么？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:35
translate chinese u19a1s2_d723442c:

    # "Dad" "I couldn't take it anymore, Son. I missed her too much."
    "Dad" "我实在受不了了，儿子。我太想她了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:36
translate chinese u19a1s2_c131eda3:

    # "Dad" "I tried to make things work with Lisa. I really did."
    "Dad" "我试着和丽莎和好。我真的试过了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:37
translate chinese u19a1s2_6b049c9b:

    # "Dad" "But she wasn't your mother."
    "Dad" "但她不是你妈妈。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:40
translate chinese u19a1s2_5cd96de1:

    # "Dad" "I found a way that I could see your mother again. And I took it."
    "Dad" "我找到了能再见到你妈妈的方法。所以我这么做了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:41
translate chinese u19a1s2_902c0ffc:

    # "Dad" "I tried to contact you before I left, but you were still mad at me. You didn't respond to any of my messages. You didn't answer my calls."
    "Dad" "我走之前试着联系过你，但你还在生我的气。你没回复我任何一条消息。 你没接我电话。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:44
translate chinese u19a1s2_55462e31:

    # "Dad" "Then, I had to take the chance. I was afraid that somebody would stop me. Or that the police would come looking for me."
    "Dad" "后来，我不得不冒险一试。我怕有人会拦住我。或者警察会来找我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:45
translate chinese u19a1s2_f4e76301:

    # "Dad" "So, I had to go."
    "Dad" "所以我只能走了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:48
translate chinese u19a1s2_27abbd22:

    # pc "Do you realize what you did to Lisa and Suzy though?"
    pc "可你意识到你对丽莎和苏茜做了什么吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:49
translate chinese u19a1s2_5c6879d8:

    # pc "What you did to me?"
    pc "你对我做了什么？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:50
translate chinese u19a1s2_1b7f10b2:

    # pc "You abandoned all of us! I mean, what the fuck, Dad?"
    pc "你抛弃了我们所有人！我是说，老爸，你他妈的到底怎么了？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:53
translate chinese u19a1s2_3b52e186:

    # "Dad" "I know. I'm sorry."
    "Dad" "我知道。我很抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:54
translate chinese u19a1s2_c502753b:

    # "Dad" "I'm not a strong man. I tried, but everything was so hard without her."
    "Dad" "我不是个坚强的人。我努力过，但没有她，一切都太难了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:57
translate chinese u19a1s2_8d1e4256:

    # "Dad" "I loved her so much. When she died, I focused everything on you."
    "Dad" "我那么爱她。她去世后，我把全部心力都放在了你身上。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:58
translate chinese u19a1s2_3d42c50e:

    # "Dad" "I didn't ever really deal with losing her. I just focused on making sure that you were okay."
    "Dad" "我从未真正面对过失去她的痛苦。我只顾着确保你过得好。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:59
translate chinese u19a1s2_4b604aa5:

    # "Dad" "Then when you left, everything came flooding back again. I couldn't deal with it, [pcname]."
    "Dad" "然后当你离开时，一切又如潮水般涌了回来。我无法承受，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:60
translate chinese u19a1s2_bfcaf31d:

    # "Dad" "I needed her."
    "Dad" "我需要她。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:63
translate chinese u19a1s2_aab2715a:

    # "Dad" "When you lose somebody you love… it changes you."
    "Dad" "当你失去所爱之人……你会变得不一样。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:64
translate chinese u19a1s2_6238b820:

    # pc "I know, Dad."
    pc "我知道，爸爸。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:67
translate chinese u19a1s2_565d58d0:

    # "Dad" "Yeah. I guess you do."
    "Dad" "是啊。我想你确实懂。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:68
translate chinese u19a1s2_cc31d9ca:

    # "Dad" "Son. I'm sorry I'm not stronger."
    "Dad" "儿子。对不起，我没能更坚强些。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:71
translate chinese u19a1s2_7c0a03f2:

    # rm "Is everything okay?"
    rm "一切都好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:72
translate chinese u19a1s2_329bc8e7:

    # "Dad" "Yeah, honey. We were just talking."
    "Dad" "嗯，亲爱的。我们只是在聊天。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:75
translate chinese u19a1s2_d2e8d1e4:

    # rm "I found some clothes that should fit him."
    rm "我找到了一些应该合身他的衣服。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:76
translate chinese u19a1s2_304b842b:

    # rm "He's a little… uh… bigger than you, but these are pretty loose, so hopefully they'll work."
    rm "他比你……呃……稍微壮一点，但这些衣服挺宽松的，希望穿得上。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:77
translate chinese u19a1s2_c1aa62c6:

    # "Dad" "I'm sure they'll be fine."
    "Dad" "我确信没问题的。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:80
translate chinese u19a1s2_28f0b39b:

    # rm "Are you hungry? You should have dinner with us. I'm making soup."
    rm "你饿了吗？要不要跟我们一起吃晚饭？我正在煮汤。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:81
translate chinese u19a1s2_efe3d272:

    # "Dad" "Yes, he's going to stay for dinner."
    "Dad" "是的，他要留下来吃晚饭。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:82
translate chinese u19a1s2_7e97bc56:

    # pc "Yeah, thanks, Mo… I mean, Emilia."
    pc "嗯，谢谢，莫……我是说，艾米莉亚。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:83
translate chinese u19a1s2_4c30b3b9:

    # rm "Okay, I'll go get everything started."
    rm "好的，我去准备一下。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:86
translate chinese u19a1s2_08706d97:

    # "I put on Dad's clothes, which fit me just fine, although getting them on was a little weird, since they have no buttons or zippers."
    "我穿上了爸爸的衣服，虽然穿起来有点怪怪的——毕竟没有扣子也没有拉链——但尺寸正好合适。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:87
translate chinese u19a1s2_983e5dc8:

    # pc "How are you so much older?"
    pc "你怎么会比我大这么多？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:88
translate chinese u19a1s2_06d4b3af:

    # "Dad" "Time works different here, I suppose. I've been here for about 15 years now."
    "Dad" "我想这里的时间流逝方式不同吧。我在这儿已经大概15年了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:89
translate chinese u19a1s2_5ce89265:

    # pc "Fifteen years!? Wow."
    pc "15年！？哇。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:90
translate chinese u19a1s2_b403d44c:

    # "Dad" "Yeah. How did you get here anyway?"
    "Dad" "是啊。话说你到底是怎么来的？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:91
translate chinese u19a1s2_3da46365:

    # pc "Whitney and I built another portal."
    pc "我和惠特尼又建了一个传送门。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:92
translate chinese u19a1s2_cfe74df5:

    # "Dad" "You met Whitney?"
    "Dad" "你见过惠特尼？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:96
translate chinese u19a1s2_5017d2dd:

    # pc "I did more than meet her."
    pc "不只是见过而已。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:97
translate chinese u19a1s2_93ef5df5:

    # "Dad" "Oh yeah?"
    "Dad" "哦，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:100
translate chinese u19a1s2_19b4b192:

    # "Dad" "Nice!"
    "Dad" "太棒了！"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:101
translate chinese u19a1s2_9dee5a20:

    # "Dad" "She was a cutie."
    "Dad" "她挺可爱的。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:103
translate chinese u19a1s2_34d11db9:

    # pc "Yeah, she helped me find you. I couldn't have done it without her."
    pc "是啊，是她帮我找到你的。没有她我做不到。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:104
translate chinese u19a1s2_3488850f:

    # "Dad" "She's a smart cookie. Smarter than me."
    "Dad" "她可聪明了，比我还聪明。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:107
translate chinese u19a1s2_5d0836a0:

    # pc "She designed this bracelet so she could bring me back."
    pc "她设计了这只手镯，就是为了能把我带回来。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:108
translate chinese u19a1s2_bea91ac4:

    # pc "It's supposed to allow her to easily lock onto my DNA signature."
    pc "这手镯本该能让她轻松锁定我的DNA信号。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:109
translate chinese u19a1s2_8c758e84:

    # "Dad" "That's a good idea."
    "Dad" "这主意不错。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:110
translate chinese u19a1s2_3d64665c:

    # pc "Although, it's supposed to be invisible. Something must have messed up when I went through the portal."
    pc "不过，它本来应该是隐形的。我穿过传送门的时候，肯定出了什么岔子。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:113
translate chinese u19a1s2_21ed62c9:

    # pc "It splits in two, so that you can wear the other part and she can bring you back as well."
    pc "手镯分成了两半，这样你戴着另一半，她也能把你带回来。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:116
translate chinese u19a1s2_66436b6b:

    # "Dad" "I'm not going back, Son."
    "Dad" "我不会回去的，儿子。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:117
translate chinese u19a1s2_1491eda3:

    # pc "What do you mean? The whole point of this was so that you could come home."
    pc "什么意思？这一切不就是为了让你回家吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:120
translate chinese u19a1s2_fe1d3e38:

    # "Dad" "I am home, Son. I'm with your mother."
    "Dad" "我已经到家了，儿子。我正和你母亲在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:121
translate chinese u19a1s2_86bc4ea0:

    # pc "It's not really her though, Dad."
    pc "但那并不是真正的她，爸爸。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:124
translate chinese u19a1s2_03229bfe:

    # "Dad" "In every way that matters, it is. That's the one thing I made sure of before I came here."
    "Dad" "在所有重要的方面，她就是。这是我来这里之前特意确认过的一件事。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:125
translate chinese u19a1s2_790f7a9a:

    # "Dad" "The whole world is different, but she's the same."
    "Dad" "整个世界都变了，但她还是那个她。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:126
translate chinese u19a1s2_6a238df6:

    # "Dad" "She thinks like your mother, she loves like your mother, she has the same smile, the same walk, the same smell."
    "Dad" "她的思维方式像你母亲，她的爱意像你母亲，她有着同样的笑容、同样的步态、同样的气息。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:127
translate chinese u19a1s2_ee7332b9:

    # "Dad" "She's not the same body that died back in our world… but I think it's the same soul."
    "Dad" "她不再是我们那个世界里逝去的那个躯体……但我认为那是同一个灵魂。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:130
translate chinese u19a1s2_b1261f24:

    # pc "So you're not coming back?"
    pc "所以你不会回去了？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:131
translate chinese u19a1s2_99d8cf49:

    # "Dad" "No, Son."
    "Dad" "不，儿子。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:132
translate chinese u19a1s2_6cc5c9d0:

    # "Dad" "But I'm really happy you came. I'm glad we get to have this talk. I'm glad I get to tell you goodbye."
    "Dad" "但我真的很高兴你来了。很高兴我们能有这次谈话。 我很高兴能向你道别。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:135
translate chinese u19a1s2_19739bd6:

    # pc "But I don't want to say goodbye, Dad."
    pc "但我不想说再见，爸爸。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:136
translate chinese u19a1s2_5246d005:

    # pc "I was shitty before. I shouldn't have left. Shouldn't have gotten mad at you for trying to find love in Lisa."
    pc "以前的我太糟糕了。我不该离开的。不该因为你试图在丽莎身上寻找爱情而对你发火。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:137
translate chinese u19a1s2_5df46abb:

    # pc "I came back for you. I came to this world to find you."
    pc "我是为了你回来的。我来到这个世界就是为了找你。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:138
translate chinese u19a1s2_598236bc:

    # pc "I don't want to lose you."
    pc "我不想失去你。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:141
translate chinese u19a1s2_d7c91541:

    # "Dad" "Oh Son, you're never going to lose me."
    "Dad" "哦，儿子，你永远不会失去我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:142
translate chinese u19a1s2_a6951b39:

    # "Dad" "I look at you and it's like looking into a mirror. You {i}are{/i} me."
    "Dad" "看着你，就像照镜子一样。你{i}就是{/i}我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:143
translate chinese u19a1s2_6e85f5c5:

    # "Dad" "All the good parts at least. And all the good parts of your mother as well."
    "Dad" "至少是所有美好的部分。还有你母亲所有美好的部分。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:144
translate chinese u19a1s2_e0f30158:

    # "Dad" "I'm sorry I haven't always been there for you. And I'm sorry I'm not going to be there for you in the future."
    "Dad" "对不起，我没能一直陪在你身边。也对不起，将来我无法再陪在你身边。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:145
translate chinese u19a1s2_6405d419:

    # "Dad" "But you don't need me, Son. You're so much smarter and stronger and more capable than I ever was."
    "Dad" "但你不需要我，儿子。你比我当年聪明得多、坚强得多、能干得多。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:148
translate chinese u19a1s2_17c3c75e:

    # "Dad" "And I love you."
    "Dad" "而且，我爱你。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:149
translate chinese u19a1s2_2077d21a:

    # pc "I love you too, Dad."
    pc "我也爱你，爸爸。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:150
translate chinese u19a1s2_23ac61f6:

    # "We just hold each other like that for a while. It's nice to feel him again, even if it might be the last time."
    "我们就那样拥抱了一会儿。能再次感受到他的存在真好，哪怕这可能是最后一次。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:153
translate chinese u19a1s2_56d527f5:

    # "Then there's a knock on the door."
    "这时，门外传来敲门声。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:154
translate chinese u19a1s2_7de852df:

    # rm "Hey guys. Dinner is almost ready."
    rm "“嘿，各位。晚饭快做好了。”"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act1/act1scene2.rpy:155
translate chinese u19a1s2_1f80a39e:

    # "Dad" "That sounds wonderful, thanks honey."
    "Dad" "“听起来真棒，谢谢亲爱的。”"

